      </figure>
      <div class="tap-indicator"></div>
      <button class="intro-demo__reset" id="intro-demo-reset">Reset</button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="g-main__item project__body streetcred__intro-content">
    <div class="streetcred__intro-container">
      <h3>Show them the foundation</h3>
      <p>
        A hard part of any app is the onboarding. You want to help folks 
        understand the object and expectations, but you don’t want to over explain. 
        People are smart. With StreetCred we needed a quick, interactive way to 
        explain the game mechanics, without slowing down first run momentum. 
      </p>
      <p>
        I designed and built the game intro that progressively displays real UI 
        elements to show how the pieces fit together. 
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

